# Media Container

## Multimedia Container

* A digital file format that holds audio, video and subtitiles.
* AVI, MKV, MPEG-4, QuickTIme
* metadata, synchronization, compression, ...
* ex\) .mp4 &gt; meta &gt; codec &gt; mdat &gt; processing

## Sequencial Media Container

* Sequencial media stream data
* MPEG\(.mpeg\), AVI\(.avi\)

## Seekable Media Container

* table-base\(index-base\) container
* QuickTime\(.mov, .qt, .moov\), MPEG-4\(.mp4\)
